âœ… No need to escape +, ?, | anymore

ğŸ§  Easy-to-Remember Cheats
Want to...	Use this
Start of line	^text
End of line	text$
Match any 1 character	.
Match 0 or more	*
Match 1 or more	+ (use \+ without -E)
Match exact word	-w
Exclude matches	-v
Color results	--color
Use extended regex	grep -E

